      <h2>What is AdLit?</h2>
      <p>AdLit  is a four-year interdisciplinary research project, financed by the IWT (Belgian agency for innovation by science and technology). AdLit is short for advertising literacy, which refers to the personal knowledge people have about advertising, its  persuasive intent, and the advertising techniques that are used to target them.</p>
